"When <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem> is enabled, wrongly "
"spelled text is underlined in the document on-the-fly."
msgstr ""
"Kada je <guimenuitem>Automatska provera pravopisa</guimenuitem> uključeno, "
"pogrešne reči u dokumentu se podvlače u letu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
