msgstr "<guimenu>Alatke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pravopis...</guimenuitem>"

# skip-rule: t-label
#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>This initiates the spellchecking program - a program designed to "
"help the user catch and correct any spelling errors.</action> Clicking on "
"this entry will start the checker and bring up the speller dialog box "
"through which the user can control the process. There are four settings "
"lined up vertically in the center of the dialog with their corresponding "
"labels just to the left. Starting at the top they are:"
msgstr ""
"<action>Pokreće pravopisar, program koji korisniku pomaže da pohvata i "
"ispravi pravopisne greške.</action> Klik na ovu stavku pokrenuće proveru i "
"dozvati dijalog kroz koji korisnik može da upravlja procesom. U dijalogu su "
"date četiri postavke. Počev od gornje:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unknown word:"
msgstr "Nepoznata reč:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1710
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, the spellchecker indicates the word currently under consideration. "
"This happens when the checker encounters a word not in its dictionary - a "
"file containing a list of correctly spelled words against which it compares "
"each word in the editor."
msgstr ""
"Ovde pravopisar daje reč koja se trenutno razmatra, tj. koja se ne nalazi u "
"njegovom rečniku (fajlu sa spiskom ispravno napisanih reči sa kojim se "
"upoređuju reči u uređivaču)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace with:"
msgstr "Zameni sa:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the checker has any similar words in its dictionary the first one will be "
"listed here. The user can accept the suggestion, type in his or her own "
"correction, or choose a different suggestion from the next box."
msgstr ""
"Ako pravopisar u svom rečniku ima neke <emphasis>slične</emphasis> reči, "
"prva će biti navedena ovde. Korisnik može prihvatiti taj predlog, upisati "
"sopstvenu ispravku, ili odabrati drugi predlog sa spiska ispod."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language:"
msgstr "Jezik:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed multiple dictionaries, here you can select which "
"dictionary/language should be used."
msgstr ""
"Ako je instalirano više rečnika, ovde možete odabrati koji rečnik-jezik "
"treba da se koristi. "

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right side of the dialog box are 6 buttons that allow the user to "
"control the spellcheck process. They are:"
msgstr ""
"Na desnoj strani dijaloga stoji šest dugmadi kojima korisnik upravlja "
"procesom provere pravopisa. Ona su:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add to Dictionary"
msgstr "Dodaj u rečnik"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing this button adds the <guilabel>Unknown word </guilabel> to the "
"checker's dictionary. This means that in the future the checker will always "
"consider this word to be correctly spelled."
msgstr ""
"Pritisak na ovo dugme dodaje nepoznatu reč u rečnik pravopisara. To znači da "
"će pravopisar ubuduće tu reč smatrati pravilno napisanom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: menus.docbook:1744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suggest"
msgstr "Predloži"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The checker may list here a number of possible replacements for the word "
"under consideration. Clicking on any one of the suggestions will cause that "
"word to be entered in the <guilabel>Replace with</guilabel> box, above."
msgstr ""
"Pravopisar ovde može nabrojati moguće zamene za reč koja se razmatra. Klikom "
"na jedan od predloga, ta reč će biti unesene u polje <guilabel>Zameni sa:</"
"guilabel> iznad."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1752
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Replace All"
msgid "Replace"
msgstr "Zameni sve"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button has the checker replace the word under consideration in the "
"document with the word in the <guilabel>Replace with</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"Ovo dugme govori pravopisaru da razmatranu reč u dokumentu zameni onom iz "
"polja <guilabel>Zameni sa:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace All"
msgstr "Zameni sve"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button causes the checker to replace not only the current "
"<guilabel>Unknown word:</guilabel> but to automatically make the same "
"substitution for any other occurrences of this <guilabel>Unknown word</"
"guilabel> in the document."
msgstr ""
"Ovo dugme čini da pravopisar zameni ne samo trenutnu nepoznatu reč, nego i "
"da automatski ponovi istu zamenu za sve druge jednake reči u dokumentu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore"
msgstr "Ignoriši"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activating this button will have the checker move on without making any "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom na ovo dugme pravopisar će nastaviti dalje bez izmene trenutne "
"reči."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1773
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore All"
msgstr "Ignoriši sve"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button tells the checker to do nothing with the current "
"<guilabel>Unknown word:</guilabel> and to pass over any other instances of "
"the same word."
msgstr ""
"Ovo dugme govori pravopisaru da ništa ne čini kako sa tekućom nepoznatom "
"reči, tako i svim ostalim primercima te reči kroz dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This only applies to the current spellcheck run. If the checker is run again "
"later it will stop on this same word."
msgstr ""
"Ovo važi samo tokom trenutne provere pravopisa. Naredna pokretanja "
"pravopisara ponovo će zastati na ovoj istoj reči."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Three more buttons are located horizontally along the bottom of the "
"spellcheck dialog. They are:"
msgstr ""
"Još tri dugmeta poređana su vodoravno duž dna dijaloga provere pravopisa. To "
"su:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1789
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1790
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This invokes the &kde; help system starting at the &kappname; help pages "
#| "(this document)."
msgid "This invokes the &kde; help system with the help page for this dialog."
msgstr ""
"Poziva <acronym>KDE‑ov</acronym> sistem pomoći, na stranicama "
"<application>K‑pisanja</application> (ovaj dokument). "

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1795
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finished"
msgstr "Gotovo"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1796
#, no-c-format
msgid "This button ends the spellcheck process, and returns to the document."
msgstr "Ovo dugme završava proces provere pravopisa i vraća se na dokument."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: menus.docbook:1801
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Odustani"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button cancels the spellcheck process, all modifications are reverted, "
"and you will return to your document."
msgstr ""
"Ovim dugmetom se odustaje od provere pravopisa. Sve izmene se bivaju "
"poništene, i vraćate se na dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1813
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spelling (from cursor)...</"
#| "guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling (from cursor)...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Alatke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pravopis (od kursora)...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program but it starts where your cursor is "
"instead of at the beginning of the document."
msgstr ""
"Pokreće pravopisar, ali tako da provera počne od položaja kursora umesto od "
"početka dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1825
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spellcheck Selection...</"
#| "guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spellcheck Selection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Alatke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Proveri pravopis izbora...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1831
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellchecks the current selection."
msgstr "Proverava pravopis trenutnog izbora."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1836
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Change Dictionary</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Change Dictionary</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Alatke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Promeni rečnik...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a drop down box with all available dictionaries for spellchecking "
"at the bottom of the editor window. This allows easy switching of the "
"spellcheck dictionary &eg; for automatic spellcheck of text in different "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje padajući spisak sa svim dostupnim rečnicima za proveru pravopisa u "
"dnu prozora uređivača. Ovako možete brzo menjati rečnike, npr. radi provere "
"teksta na različitim jezicima."

